DESCRIPTION:Meet at the Bullitt Fireplace Trailhead on Mountainside drive. 
	There's plenty of parking along Mountainside drive. Bring a headlamp for t
	he run. Join us after the run for our weekly potluck. Bring a potluck dish
	 with a serving utensils\, and your own dish and utensil.  Route: Main Rou
	te: This route is 6mi with 1600ft of gain. The run starts with most the ve
	rt up to the microwave\, and heads down Chybinski trail.  Route:  https://
