UID:Is7lpOKLs5KpMEVOsZa0Y
SUMMARY:Volpone
DTSTAMP:20260315T013214Z
DTSTART:20260324T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Volpone \\(The Fox\\)\, a wealthy Venetian\, lusts for yet more
	 gold\, and with the help of his devious brilliant servant Mosca \\(The Fl
	y\\)\, delights in finding ways to steal it from his wealthy\, corrupt Ven
	etian neighbors. Ben Jonson’s renowned 1606 comedy takes us on a wild funn
	y ride with one of the greatest plots in all theatre through a greedy mad 
	society where self-interest is the only real value\, and deception the onl
	y truth. And where the greatest pleasure of all is…THE GRIFT.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/volpone/18184142/2026-03-23T00\n\nFro
	m SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
